            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Each node can be expanded to reveal more details or branch into new directions, creating a rich web of connected knowledge.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 w-full">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl relative group">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img
                  src="/images/graph.webp"
                  alt="Interactive Graph"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
<!-- Showcase 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Beyond Traditional Chat</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Traditional AI chat interfaces present knowledge as linear walls of text. Dialectic's graph-based approach structures information spatially.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
              This allows for non-linear exploration while maintaining context, making it easier to revisit specific points and see the big picture.
            </p>
